	"name": {
		"en-US": "The Fathers of the Church"
	},
	"description": {
		"en-US": "The voice of the early Church — Greek, Latin, Syriac — in the canonical 19th-century English translations (Ante-Nicene Fathers and Nicene & Post-Nicene Fathers, edited by Roberts/Donaldson and Philip Schaff)."
	},
	"icon": "book",
	"languages": [
		"en-US"
